-- U.S. Chlorine Plants Ran at 82% of Capacity in February
-- B y   J a c k   K a s k e y
-- 2013-03-21T15:18:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-21/u-s-chlorine-plants-ran-at-82-of-capacity-in-february.html
The U.S. chlorine industry operated
at 82 percent of capacity in February compared with 85 percent a
year earlier, the U.S. Chlorine Institute said.  The January operating rate was 78 percent, the institute
said today in an e-mail.  To contact the reporter on this story:
